==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Neocriticism
<hw>Ne`o*crit"i*cism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Neo-</ets> + <ets>classicism</ets>.]</ety> <def>The form of
Neo-Kantianism developed by French idealists, following <person>C.
Renouvier</person>. It rejects the noumena of <persfn>Kant</persfn>,
restricting knowledge to phenomena as constituted by a priori
categories.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

